title: THE STARFISH AND THE SPIDER
description: THE UNSTOPPABLE POWER OF LEADERLESS ORGANIZATIONS                               This book is about what happens when there&#039;s no one in charge. It&#039;s about what happens when there&#039;s no hierarchy. You&#039;d think there would be disorder, even chaos.
